data.description: Welcome to this stunning 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home located in a desirable gated community. This property boasts newer flooring throughout the living area, creating a modern and stylish ambiance. Enjoy the spacious front and back porches, perfect for relaxation and entertaining. With no front or rear neighbors, you'll enjoy added privacy and tranquility. The kitchen features a beautiful Corian counter, adding a touch of elegance to your culinary space. Additionally, this home offers picturesque views of the golf course from both the front and back yard, providing a serene and picturesque setting. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exceptional property your own!
